summary: Savegame with non-quest Alchemy combines already discovered
descriptionHtml:
I was getting tired of having to re-discover  all of the propertys of the alchemy ingredients each time I wanted to make a new player So I Created this savegame to start off from And thought many would find it useful 

I couldn\'t find a fast way of discovering all the alchemy combines so I spent my time combining all known non-quest ingredients together , they should not only have all there propertys discovered - but should grey out all non-collectable ingredients when selected

all ready for you to use SHOWRACEMENU and start your new player with a full knowledge of alchemy combines
author: j_kr76
